      "content": "i get the \"balance\" thing but it feels like a bit of an answer to avoid the actual question lol. like if u had to pick which one is more important for a functioning democracy, protecting those individual religious rights or making sure the law applies to everyone equally regardless of faith? which one is the \"right\" priority?",
